\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "Fushiki:2016ji"

\end_inset

).
 These studies also, highlight the the fact that some of these fundamental
 sensory transformations are likely conserved across invertebrates and vertebrat
es (
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "borst_common_2015"

\end_inset

).
 
\end_layout

